{"tid":1634203,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果覺得裝修太暴力唔好睇，不如暫時改為全力封印＋貼符！","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T06:34:26.000Z","uid":34241,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"225472926de9c05db7379fa7250a9cd884180b49","tid":1634203,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"裝修既目的係想懲戒、阻嚇對方，等對方開唔到門做唔到生意、唔可以再為禍香港　<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但全套裝修只係其中一個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家仲可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全力封印</strong></span></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>暫時唔做裝修佬，轉做封印師！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大力裝修又多掣肘，又多顧慮<br />\n咁就暫時轉職做封印師！<br />\n可達目的又不會得失支持者！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵咁鍾意落閘封站封出口，我地幫佢封！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有出口一律封印！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用所有方法封閘！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n封印鐵閘又好，話之你起磚牆落石屎都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n總之就完全封印佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑紅藍黃分類大法<br />\n黑、紅：全力封印，滴水不漏（銀行唔好全部封哂，留返幾間比班藍絲排下隊攞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n藍：另類封印，齋坐不消費（參考元氣下午茶）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>遍地開花！全力封印！<br />\n簡單封印法，人人都做到！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不過留意返，<br />\n封印術只係短暫措施，<br />\n對家好快翻生，<br />\n所以要每日快閃封印<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">參考功略<br />\n<blockquote>[GTA攻略：結界師／封印師] 幫港鐵封站，防止武裝恐怖份子衝出襲擊市民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/egNfmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/egNfmS</a><br />\n<br />\n[GTA攻略：天道師] 其實執行天道既時候可以做多少少野黎昇華整個行動（主要做比外界睇）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614312</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n（歡迎貼多Ｄ攻略LINK)</span>"},{"pid":"6623a636df9913106cb2d2803544d63a181aa4a5","tid":1634203,"uid":159762,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=4f33b1ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"bd7d0cdf991e00f255556aa60842426ad6d7b87a","tid":1634203,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"全民封印 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e765e1b8ddde7f8db18644f2274c7546d82621","tid":1634203,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:08:22.000Z","msg":"學術台冇人睇？"},{"pid":"daa596b5dba478b5f5c806b5ec9ab91b66ee26e2","tid":1634203,"uid":239384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:10:25.000Z","msg":"冇裝修呀 唔比你入姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa04ad5080003cbfe9f9e0244c338ef203ec8344","tid":1634203,"uid":20076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"封"},{"pid":"3bfc94a07095f7ef1b00f60ae06ca44229f82994","tid":1634203,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:13:50.00